#10601
Graveyard, Northwest Corner~
The trees curve towards the south and east here. The neighboring
forest emits a scent of fresh air and pine trees. One might think
that it is pretty safe here, if it weren't for the headstones
which for some reason add a very sepulchral tone to the area.
Scattered patches of shrubbery clutter the ground, causing you
to have to watch your step so you don't fall.
~
