#10602
Graveyard~
Several fancy headstones lie peacefully on the ground, bringing
fears of death, and the unknown. Hopefully you don't find your
own name here any time soon. Moss covers most anything you happen
to glance at, and gives your surroundings the feel of age.
Just to the north of you is where the old church used to be.  But
that was as long ago as when the town well used to be filled up to the
top with water.
~
