#10609
Graveyard~
Your eyes fall upon a tombstone that stands out amongst the others
because it is crooked.  It is said that knocking over a tombstone
is bad luck. Better not test that saying. Bad luck is something
that you definitely don't want in a place like this.  You also
see several flowers adorning a tombstone just next to the crooked
one. They smell quite sweet.
