Graveyard~
Directly to the east there is a dark hole in the woods that seems
large enough to fit through. Glancing into the hole you see nothing
but darkness. A small ways to the west a small patch of berry bushes
have grown. They seem to be the only fruit-bearing bush in the area.
Despite the urge to go and taste the berries, you feel compelled
to leave the graveyard. The thought of so many dead bodies beneath
your feet is unnerving.
