#10618
New Hope, Near a Dark Tunnel~
Two large willow trees cover the area with their flimsy branches,
causing a nice shadowy covering from the elements. To the northwest
A narrow, dark tunnel leads to New Hope's graveyard. Many a rumor
has been heard about the ghastly inhabitants of the cemetary, it
would be a horrifying experience to live out one of those rumors.
Your better judgement warns you to stay away.
