#10619
Graveyard, at the old cathedral~
The wind is cold and the setting of things is very uneasy.  Here
stands the old cathedral, pre-church to the one now set in town.
It is older than most anyone in the world minus the gods themselves.
No one knows what happened to it exactly, but it just must be evil.
The ruins look to be for the most part unsafe to the smaller person, 
though if you are built in strength it may be worth a look around,
the steps are right in front of you.
~
